{"tid":126020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠表示不會提名任何特首候選人惟會投票","createTime":"2017-02-19T04:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T08:25:52.000Z","uid":55299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0e99e846101e4b28b1c124b3fc7123198bf0d7","tid":126020,"uid":55299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=924111&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D924111%26csid%3D261_341&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b760cf33\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=924111&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n長和系主席李嘉誠出席汕頭大學活動後表示，幾位特首參選人都是熟朋友，他一早宣布不會為任何參選人提名，但一定會投票，指提名會得罪人，提名任何一位，都會損害其他三位，他認為特首人選有兩個原則，包括好好落實一國兩制及法治，而四位來說都做得到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c863d37ed1c008edbd546835dc9ad911cb0eeed","tid":126020,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=924111&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D924111%26csid%3D261_341&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b760cf33\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=924111&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n長和系主席李嘉誠出席汕頭大學活動後表示，幾位特首參選人都是熟朋友，他一早宣布不會為任何參選人提名，但一定會投票，指提名會得罪人，提名任何一位，都會損害其他三位，他認為特首人選有兩個原則，包括好好落實一國兩制及法治，而四位來說都做得到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識自保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 提名林鄭有可能損害同習大大既感情,提名其他人又會得罪江派689林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60ff8bd7b2a7f